Build
-----
- set SCALE_SYS environmental variable (see the sysdef directory)
 % SCALE_SYS=Linux64-gnu-ompi (example)

- make dc_utils library
 % cd dc_uitls
 % make

- make gtool library
 % cd gtool
 % make

- make scalelib library
 % cd scalelib/src
 % make depend
 % make

- make and run the test cases of scale-les
 % cd scale-les/test/case/hydrostatic/500m (example)
 % make
 % make run
